SUMMARY:Total Solar Eclipse ("Eclipse of the Century") 2027
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270802
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270803
DTSTAMP:20260721T000000Z
UID:total-solar-eclipse-eclipse-of-the-century-2027-2027-08-02@space-scien
 ce.pyros-world-events-calendar
DESCRIPTION:CONFIRMED. Longest totality of the century (up to 6m22s near L
 uxor\, Egypt)\; path crosses Spain\, Gibraltar\, Morocco\, Algeria\, Libya
 \, Egypt\, Saudi Arabia\, Yemen\, Somalia. Longest total eclipse visible f
 rom land until 2114.\nSource: https://www.timeanddate.com/eclipse/solar/20
 27-august-2\nVerified: 2026-07-21
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.timeanddate.com/eclipse/solar/2027-august-2
END:VEVENT
